<plot>In the near future, a man-made virus is unleashed into the atmosphere; killing most of the world's population... of women. Alex, searches for a rogue scientist in the mountains, who may or may not have a cure to save his wife. Jake, an empathetic widower, offers Alex food and shelter up at his cabin. A haunted cabin; a mysterious doll; and a man's obsession to bring back the dead... will test Alex and Jake's will... as they fight to survive and be... the last piece standing.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?569675</url></doc>
